{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──半年后。\n整骨院依旧勉强维持着经营。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "欢迎光临。今天也是准时到呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "时间就是金钱嘛。一分一秒都不想浪费。……快，赶紧开始吧。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（半年了，每周都雷打不动地来。台风天也来了。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "今天也是老样子？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "嗯。肩膀和腰，重点做。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "明白了。那先换衣服吧。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──治疗中"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "肩胛骨内侧又僵了呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "……年末贷款申请多。文件工作增加了。",
      "outfit": "bikini"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "高利贷年末也忙啊。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "别叫高利贷。是借贷业。",
      "outfit": "bikini"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "好好。……这里按一下。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "……唔。",
      "outfit": "bikini"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（……刚才，肩膀微微颤了一下。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（那12周的条件反射，应该还残留了一点吧……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……怎么了。手停了啊。",
      "outfit": "bikini"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "不，没什么。继续了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（……如果当时再进一步的话，也许会变成不一样的关系吧。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（……算了，这样也挺好的。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──治疗后"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "呼。……啊，舒服多了。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "辛苦了。下周也是同一时间？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "那当然。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "…………。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……喂。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "嗯？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "下周日有赛马。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "要去吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "上次最后一场输的要赢回来。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "这话您不是从三个月前就开始说了吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "吵死了。这次一定行。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "明白了。那周日见。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──又过了几个月"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（最近，龙姐来的时间段没法安排其他预约了。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（原因很简单。手下开着黑色轿车来接她，其他客人吓得全跑了。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "嗯。……今天怎么这么空。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "是啊，嗯……"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（说不出口。绝对不能说是因为您。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "closeeyes",
      "text": "跟包场似的，不挺好嘛。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（……一点都不好啊，从经营角度来说。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（不过嘛……多亏龙姐每周都来，才没有倒闭，这也是事实。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "走了。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "辛苦了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "…………。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "closeeyes",
      "text": "……下周也来。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "好。下周见。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "每周的治疗，偶尔的赛马。\n高利贷的老板和整骨师之间，这种不可思议的关系在继续着。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "说不上更多，也说不上更少，\n但还不错——我这么觉得。",
      "triggerEnding": "normal"
    }
  ]
}
